  "title": "Social Work Associate [Buangkok / Social Science]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct needs assessments to develop appropriate programs, including evaluating and managing risks.</li>\n  <li>Plan, lead, and facilitate various programs.</li>\n  <li>Use assessment tools to develop and evaluate group work outcomes.</li>\n  <li>Create and implement group processes and specialized intervention strategies.</li>\n  <li>Facilitate, assess, and review group therapy sessions to ensure they meet the needs of residents.</li>\n  <li>Apply restorative practices, including planning and facilitating restorative circles.</li>\n  <li>Support case management by preparing for and attending all necessary case-related meetings, and maintain strong working relationships with stakeholders, including parents and schools.</li>\n  <li>Complete all required documentation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Social Sciences with experience in mentoring and working with youths.</li>\n  <li>Prior experience working with youth-at-risk is advantageous.</li>\n  <li>Strong engagement and facilitation skills.</li>\n  <li>Good knowledge and experience with social work interventions, social policies, and community engagement.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and writing skills.</li>\n</ul>",
